  ('social-worker-moex-06457', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-103-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '近年來，臺灣地區越來越重視安寧療護，各大醫院陸續成立安寧療護中心。安寧照護強調所謂「四全」 照顧，此「四全」指的是下列那「四全」？', '["「全人」、「全家」、「全隊」、「全程」", "「全人」、「全家」、「全心」、「全程」", "「全身」、「全家」、「全心」、「全程」", "「全人」、「全家」、「全院」、「全程」"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a3d845e75c7c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ca9f253103ce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "110", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-06458', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-103-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Barbara Solomon在1976年出版的「Black Empowerment: Social Work in Oppressed Communities」書中開 始使用「增強權能」這個名詞。下列那一個概念不是她書中主要的概念？', '["無力感", "制度性種族主義", "高層次的同理心", "壓迫與疏離"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:34+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a3d845e75c7c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ca9f253103ce", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103100", "c": "110", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技醫師中醫師分階段、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師、法醫師語言聽力牙體技術師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
